instruction: Transform /Users/zakariahachm/Downloads/atl_zoo/PathExp2PetriNet/Models/petrinet-example.xmi to XML model and then Transform /Users/zakariahachm/Downloads/atl_zoo/Grafcet2PetriNet/Models/PNML2XML_example.xmi to PNML model
Transform /Users/zakariahachm/Downloads/atl_zoo/Make2Ant/example/makeFileMake.xmi to Ant model and then transform /Users/zakariahachm/Downloads/atl_zoo/Ant2Maven/example/build1Ant.xmi to Maven model

- Apply /Users/zakariahachm/Downloads/atl_zoo/Grafcet2PetriNet/Models/XML2PNML_example.xmi → XML model
- Apply /Users/zakariahachm/Downloads/atl_zoo/Grafcet2PetriNet/Models/PNML2XML_example.xmi → PNML model

Apply /Users/zakariahachm/Downloads/atl_zoo/DSLBridge/MetamodelBridge/Models/SimpleExample/DSL2EMF/SimpleExampleMM-DSL.xmi to produce a KM3 model, and then apply /Users/zakariahachm/Downloads/atl_zoo/KM32Problem/Models/test-KM3.xmi to produce a Problem model

Transform /Users/zakariahachm/Downloads/atl_zoo/UML2KM3/ExampleUML.xmi to KM3 model
Transform /Users/zakariahachm/Downloads/atl_zoo/KM32EMF/Sample-KM3.xmi to EMF model

Transform the PathExp model at /Users/zakariahachm/Downloads/atl_zoo/PathExp2PetriNet/Models/pathexp-example.xmi into a PetriNet model, and then Convert the PetriNet model at /Users/zakariahachm/Downloads/atl_zoo/PathExp2PetriNet/Models/petrinet-example.xmi into a PathExp model.

Transform /Users/zakariahachm/Downloads/atl_zoo/PathExp2PetriNet/Models/petrinet-example.xmi to XML model
Restore /Users/zakariahachm/Downloads/atl_zoo/PathExp2PetriNet/Models/xml-example.xmi to PetriNet model

Transform the PNML model at /Users/zakariahachm/Downloads/atl_zoo/Grafcet2PetriNet/Models/XML2PNML_example.xmi to an XML model; then convert the XML model at /Users/zakariahachm/Downloads/atl_zoo/KMLInjector/InputModels/example-XML.xmi to a KML model.

- Transform /Users/zakariahachm/Downloads/atl_zoo/Maven2Ant/example/mavenFile.xmi to an Ant model.
- Transform /Users/zakariahachm/Downloads/atl_zoo/Make2Ant/example/antFile.xmi to an XML model.

Apply /Users/zakariahachm/Downloads/atl_zoo/IntroducePrimaryKey/with_context/build_example.xml to produce a PrimaryKeyModel, and then apply /Users/zakariahachm/Downloads/atl_zoo/EliminateRedundantInheritance/with_context/InputModels/example-KM3.xmi to produce an InheritanceCleanedModel.
